== 2008年噴發 ==
2008年4月30日，沉睡了 9,428（±75）年之久的'''柴滕火山'''出現活動現像。

5月2日當地時間 00:30 左右，'''柴滕火山'''開始噴發，鄰近10公里處的柴滕鎮及附近居民，在睡夢中被驚醒，智利政府下達緊急疏散，當地4,200名居民帶著簡單的家當，遷往臨時避難所，5月3日完成遷徙計劃<ref>{{es}}{{cite press release|title=MINISTRO DEL INTERIOR EN CHAITÉN: “ES UN ÉXITO SIN PRECEDENTES HABER EVACUADO EN 24 HORAS A CUATRO MIL PERSONAS” |publisher=ONEMI |date=2008-05-03 |url=http://www.onemi.cl/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=1418&Itemid=19 |language=es |accessdate=2008-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080611135804/http://www.onemi.cl/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=1418&Itemid=19 |archivedate=2008-06-11 }}</ref>，1名 92歲老婦人，在遷移過程中因心臟和呼吸出現異常而身亡<ref name="patagonia">{{en}}{{cite news|first=Matt |last=Malinowski |authorlink= |title=Evacuations continue in Chile volcano zone |url=http://www.patagoniatimes.cl/content/view/489/1/ |work= |publisher=Patagonia Times |date=2008-05-05 |accessdate=2008-05-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080509110013/http://www.patagoniatimes.cl/content/view/489/1/ |archivedate=2008-05-09 }}</ref><ref name="reuters">{{en}}{{cite news |title=One dead as Chilean volcano spews ash for third day |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/scienceNews/idUKN0221354320080504 |work=Reuters UK |publisher=Thomson Reuters |date=2008-05-04 |accessdate=2008-05-13 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027162231/https://uk.reuters.com/article/scienceNews/idUKN0221354320080504 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

5月3日至5月5日，[[火山灰|火山塵灰]]持續噴發，順著風勢綿延，學校與機場陸續關閉，遠至120公里外的富塔萊烏富小鎮（{{Lang-es|[[:es:Futaleufú_(comuna)|comuna Futaleufú]]}}），累積的火山塵灰厚達30至40公分，居民也被逼疏散<ref name="patagonia" /><ref name=NOW>{{cite news |url=http://www.nownews.com/2008/05/08/334-2271996.htm |title=智利沙伊頓火山至今發威不止‧鄰國阿根廷也受火山灰波及 |author=國際中心 |date=2008-05-08 |accessdate=2008-05-10}}</ref><ref>{{es}}{{cite press release|title=Informe Nª- 248 04/05/08- Actividad Volcánica (Actualiza Información) |publisher=ONEMI |date=2008-05-04 |url=http://www.onemi.cl/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=1420&Itemid=19 |language=es |accessdate=2008-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080611134215/http://www.onemi.cl/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=1420&Itemid=19 |archivedate=2008-06-11 }}</ref>。

5月6日當地時間 08:45 左右，突然劇烈爆發出[[岩漿|岩漿]]和火山塵灰，政府再度撤離火山週圍三十公里的所有軍警居民<ref>{{es}}{{cite press release|title=Informe N°251 06/05/08 Se evacua de manera preventiva totalidad de personas en Chaitén |publisher=ONEMI |date=2008-05-06 |url=http://www.onemi.cl/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=1423&Itemid=19 |language=es |accessdate=2008-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081226062735/http://www.onemi.cl/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=1423&Itemid=19 |archivedate=2008-12-26 }}</ref>。當天數度劇烈爆發，[[人造衛星|人造衛星]]空照圖顯示，大量的[[火山灰|火山塵灰]]噴上 {{convert|30|km|mi|0}}高空，飄越[[阿根廷|阿根廷]][[聖荷赫盆地|聖荷赫盆地]]（{{Lang-en|[[:en:San_Jorge_Basin|San Jorge Basin]]}}）到達[[大西洋|大西洋]]<ref>{{es}}{{cite press release|title=Informe N°252 06/05/08 - Se activan todos los operativos de evacuación en Chaitén |publisher=ONEMI |date=2008-05-06 |url=http://www.onemi.cl/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=1424&Itemid=19 |language=es |accessdate=2008-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081226062741/http://www.onemi.cl/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=1424&Itemid=19 |archivedate=2008-12-26 }}</ref>。

5月21日，一個新的[[火山穹丘|火山穹丘]]出現在火山口<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=SI/USGS Weekly Volcanic Activity Reports - Chaitén |publisher=Global Volcanism Programme |date=2008-05-27 |url=http://www.volcano.si.edu/world/volcano.cfm?vnum=1508-041&volpage=weekly |accessdate=2008-07-10 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024233355/https://volcano.si.edu/world/volcano.cfm?vnum=1508-041&volpage=weekly |dead-url=no }}</ref>，5月24日高度已超高舊的穹丘<ref>{{es}}{{cite press release |title=Actividad Eruptiva del Volcán Chaitén ha Decaído al Tipo Subpliniano |publisher=SERNAGEOMIN |date=2008-05-26 |url=http://www.sernageomin.cl/index.php?plantilla=detalle&option=com_content&task=view&id=306&Itemid=4&sectionid=4 |language=es |accessdate=2008-07-10 |archive-date=2017-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170411220549/http://www.sernageomin.cl/index.php?plantilla=detalle&option=com_content&task=view&id=306&Itemid=4&sectionid=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。剛開始時，穹丘在火山口北邊發展<ref>{{es}}{{cite press release |title=Informa Acerca de Actividad Eruptiva del volcán Chaitén |publisher=SERNAGEOMIN |date=2008-05-22 |url=http://www.sernageomin.cl/index.php?plantilla=detalle&option=com_content&task=view&id=304&Itemid=4&sectionid=4 |language=es |accessdate=2008-07-10 |archive-date=2017-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170411135950/http://www.sernageomin.cl/index.php?plantilla=detalle&option=com_content&task=view&id=304&Itemid=4&sectionid=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>6月11日左右，在舊的穹丘上，出現另外兩新的噴孔<ref>{{es}}{{cite press release |title=Volcán Chaitén Presentó Aumento de Actividad Eruptiva |publisher=SERNAGEOMIN |date=2008-06-13 |url=http://www.sernageomin.cl/index.php?plantilla=detalle&option=com_content&task=view&id=313&Itemid=2&sectionid=4 |language=es |accessdate=2008-07-10 |archive-date=2017-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170411140606/http://www.sernageomin.cl/index.php?plantilla=detalle&option=com_content&task=view&id=313&Itemid=2&sectionid=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，一個往西、一個向南發展，結果堵塞了山下的[[排水溝|排水溝]]<ref>{{es}}{{cite press release |title=Informa Acerca de Actividad Eruptiva del Volcán Chaitén |publisher=SERNAGEOMIN |date=2008-06-22 |url=http://www.sernageomin.cl/index.php?plantilla=detalle&option=com_content&task=view&id=316&Itemid=4&sectionid=4 |language=es |accessdate=2008-07-10 |archive-date=2017-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170411140609/http://www.sernageomin.cl/index.php?plantilla=detalle&option=com_content&task=view&id=316&Itemid=4&sectionid=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="SNGM080703">{{es}}{{cite press release |title=informa sobre el volcán Chaitén |publisher=[[:en:Servicio_nacional_de_geología_y_minería|SERNAGEOMIN]] |date=2008-07-03 |url=http://www.sernageomin.cl/index.php?plantilla=detalle&option=com_content&task=view&id=326&Itemid=2&sectionid=4 |language=es |accessdate=2008-07-11 |archive-date=2017-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170411141047/http://www.sernageomin.cl/index.php?plantilla=detalle&option=com_content&task=view&id=326&Itemid=2&sectionid=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=SI/USGS Weekly Volcanic Activity Reports - Chaitén |publisher=Global Volcanism Programme |date=2008-07-08 |url=http://www.volcano.si.edu/world/volcano.cfm?vnum=1508-041&volpage=weekly |accessdate=2008-07-12 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024233355/https://volcano.si.edu/world/volcano.cfm?vnum=1508-041&volpage=weekly |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

8月5日，火山穹丘漸時停止噴發，究研人員坐直昇機視察<ref>{{es}}{{cite web |url=http://www.sernageomin.cl/index.php?plantilla=detalle&option=com_content&task=view&id=340&Itemid=2&sectionid=4 |title=Informa Acerca de la Actividad Eruptiva de los volcanes Chaitén y Llaima |date=2008-08-05 |language=es |accessdate=2008-08-08 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304192634/http://www.sernageomin.cl/index.php?plantilla=detalle&option=com_content&task=view&id=340&Itemid=2&sectionid=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 造成損害 ===
柴滕火山山坡及附近的樹林，被火山噴出岩礫所焚毁<ref>{{es}}{{cite press release |title=Informa acerca del Volcán Chaitén |publisher=SERNAGEOMIN |date=2008-06-05 |url=http://www.sernageomin.cl/index.php?plantilla=detalle&option=com_content&task=view&id=309&Itemid=4&sectionid=4 |language=es |accessdate=2008-07-10 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303191328/http://www.sernageomin.cl/index.php?plantilla=detalle&option=com_content&task=view&id=309&Itemid=4&sectionid=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[智利|智利]]全國與[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]南部大部份地區，被[[火山灰|火山灰]]所覆蓋，對農業產生長遠的影響。

5月12日開始，柴滕鎮被火山泥流侵害<ref>{{es}}{{cite press release|title=Informe N° 270 12/05/08 Actividad Volcán Chaitén ( Actualiza Información) |publisher=ONEMI |date=2008-05-12 |url=http://www.onemi.cl/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=1442&Itemid=19 |language=es |accessdate=2008-07-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080616065026/http://www.onemi.cl/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=1442&Itemid=19 |archivedate=2008-06-16 }}</ref>，破壞了許多的建築物，把流經鎮上的柴滕河填滿，數週之後，新的河道出現，並破壞了鎮上的道路與建築物。

